data.description: Assumable FHA loan at a 5.625% interest rate possible, inquire for details.  Come see this beautiful Washougal home on a large lot with views of Orchard Hills Country Club.  This property sits on a quiet cul-de-sac and has a year round creek in the backyard.  The home features an updated kitchen with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances, large primary suite with walk in closet, two cedar decks with territorial and golf course views, central A/C, main floor office,  fiber cement siding and much more.
